Author: lonelybeet
Text: Not here no, this is a place more for harm reduction and support. This subreddit is more of a place to commiserate the pains of having a mental illness, not a place where we urge each other to meet our weight loss goals.   An older subreddit was banned for being seemingly "pro" ED so we try to avoid that as much as possible now.  Maybe try the creepy lion's dens at r/fasting or r/1200isplenty
